Package cetus.hir

Class SomeExpression

  • java.lang.Object
    • cetus.hir.Expression
      • cetus.hir.SomeExpression
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Printable, Traversable, java.lang.Cloneable, java.lang.Comparable<Expression>
    public class SomeExpression
extends Expression
    Represents a container that holds a raw code not expressed as a well-defined internal representation. Non-standard GCC extension such as inline assembly is represented with this expression.
